<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-3456] Error when creation a variable named &quot;context&quot;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-3456</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;it looks like when we create a variable with name &quot;context&quot; we break the shell.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To reproduce the error just create a variable called &quot;context&quot; and not will work. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you set the context variable to null it will work again.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example bellow.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Groovy Shell (1.6.0, JVM: 1.6.0_07)&lt;br/&gt;
Type &apos;help&apos; or &apos;\h&apos; for help.&lt;br/&gt;
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;br/&gt;
groovy:000&amp;gt; //this works&lt;br/&gt;
===&amp;gt; true&lt;br/&gt;
groovy:000&amp;gt; a = 1&lt;br/&gt;
===&amp;gt; 1&lt;br/&gt;
groovy:000&amp;gt; //after this, error!!&lt;br/&gt;
===&amp;gt; true&lt;br/&gt;
groovy:000&amp;gt; context = &quot;context&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
===&amp;gt; context&lt;br/&gt;
ERROR org.codehaus.groovy.runtime.typehandling.GroovyCastException: Cannot cast&lt;br/&gt;
object &apos;context&apos; with class &apos;java.lang.String&apos; to class &apos;groovy.lang.Binding&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
        at java_lang_Runnable$run.call (Unknown Source)&lt;br/&gt;
groovy:000&amp;gt; a = 1&lt;br/&gt;
===&amp;gt; 1&lt;br/&gt;
ERROR org.codehaus.groovy.runtime.typehandling.GroovyCastException: Cannot cast&lt;br/&gt;
object &apos;context&apos; with class &apos;java.lang.String&apos; to class &apos;groovy.lang.Binding&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
        at java_lang_Runnable$run.call (Unknown Source)&lt;br/&gt;
groovy:000&amp;gt; purge all&lt;br/&gt;
ERROR org.codehaus.groovy.runtime.typehandling.GroovyCastException: Cannot cast&lt;br/&gt;
object &apos;context&apos; with class &apos;java.lang.String&apos; to class &apos;groovy.lang.Binding&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
        at java_lang_Runnable$run.call (Unknown Source)&lt;br/&gt;
groovy:000&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
